### Response Schema

{% include '_generic_v4_response.md.j2' %}

#### data

| Field      | Type  | Non-null | Description                                |
|------------|-------|----------|--------------------------------------------|
| field_list | array | Yes      | Context field list. Each element represents one context data entry. See field_list element definition |

#### field_list Element

| Field       | Type   | Non-null | Description                                                  |
|-------------|--------|----------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| name        | string | Yes      | Name of a context data entry, used to identify the data item |
| value       | string | Yes      | Value of a context data entry                                |
| description | string | Yes      | Description of a context data entry, explaining its meaning  |

